<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِالأَْيَّامِ، فَيَكْمُل بِالثَّالِثِ وَهَكَذَا <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالظَّاهِرُ أَنَّ هَذَا الْخِلاَفَ يَجْرِي فِي كُل مَا يُعْتَبَرُ بِالأَْشْهُرِ، كَعِدَّةِ وَفَاةٍ، وَصَوْمِ شَهْرَيْ كَفَّارَةٍ، وَمُدَّةِ خِيَارٍ، وَأَجَل ثَمَنٍ وَسَلَمٍ لأَِنَّ هَذِهِ الْمَسَائِل تُسَاوِي مَا تَقَدَّمَ مَعْنًى <span class="c2">(٢)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الشَّهْرُ الْحَرَامُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> الأَْشْهُرُ الْحُرُمُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>شَهْرُ رَمَضَانَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> رَمَضَانُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>شُهْرَةٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> تَسَامُحٌ، أَلْبِسَةٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
